The CV curves comparison between MoS2 foam and reference MoS2 bulk is shown in Supplementary Figs. 15 and 4b. The presence of the two pairs of redox peaks points to a different redox reaction pathway in MoS2 foam. As indicated in Supplementary Figs. 15a and 4b, the first cycle of CV curves emanated from the MoS2 bulk standard demonstrates the well-studied four-electron reduction reaction (4Li++ MoS2 + 4e−↔\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
